documents.title: About Me
documents.content: I am Lakshmipriya RajeshKanna, a software engineer with a Master’s from Drexel University. I specialize in full-stack web development, DevOps, and AI-powered systems. I am experienced in Python, Java, JavaScript, React, Spring Boot, SQL, and cloud platforms like AWS.
